title: Stormwater inlets, drains and catch basins
description: The catch basin data is collected by SFDPW Hydraulics Engineering and SFPUC Wastewater Enterprise, Collection System Division engineers, drafters and operators.  The data is collected from sewer reference and construction documents and field surveys. You can learn more about how the City's wastewater collection system works here: http://www.sfwater.org/index.aspx?page=399
